## ── Security headers — all pages ──
/*
  # Prevent clickjacking
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  # Prevent MIME-type sniffing
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  # Control referrer information
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  # HSTS — force HTTPS for 1 year (includeSubDomains, preload-ready)
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  # Permissions policy — restrict sensitive APIs
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=(), usb=(), bluetooth=(), interest-cohort=()
  # Cross-Origin Opener Policy — prevents cross-origin window attacks
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
  # Cross-Origin Resource Policy — only same-site can load our resources
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-site
  # X-XSS-Protection — disabled (modern browsers use CSP; old IE mode=block can cause issues)
  X-XSS-Protection: 0
  # Content Security Policy — consolidated (single source of truth)
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self' https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://unpkg.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://tagmanager.google.com https://js.stripe.com https://*.supabase.co https://connect.facebook.net https://www.clarity.ms https://*.clarity.ms; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://unpkg.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com data:; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://www.google-analytics.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://lh3.googleusercontent.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://twemoji.maxcdn.com https://*.googleapis.com https://*.supabase.co https://www.facebook.com https://connect.facebook.net https://unpkg.com https://*.basemaps.cartocdn.com https://i.ytimg.com https://img.youtube.com https://yt3.ggpht.com https://*.ggpht.com https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net https://static-cdn.kick.com https://files.kick.com https://kick.com https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; connect-src 'self' https://*.netlify.app https://*.netlify.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://region1.google-analytics.com https://analytics.google.com https://www.google.com https://fonts.googleapis.com https://fonts.gstatic.com https://open.er-api.com https://api.frankfurter.app https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://api.coingecko.com https://api.coincap.io https://zpclagtgczsygrgztlts.supabase.co https://*.supabase.co wss://*.supabase.co https://api.anthropic.com https://*.googleapis.com https://www.facebook.com https://connect.facebook.net https://www.clarity.ms https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; frame-src https://js.stripe.com; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self' https://formspree.io; upgrade-insecure-requests

## ── Embeddable widget iframes — allow cross-origin framing ──
## These pages are a public embed product: any publisher may <iframe> them.
## We relax framing to `frame-ancestors *` here ONLY, and override the inherited
## `X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN`. Browsers ignore X-Frame-Options whenever a CSP
## `frame-ancestors` directive is present (CSP2 precedence), so frame-ancestors is
## authoritative; the X-Frame-Options override is defense in depth for the replace
## case. The full CSP is repeated so this works whether Netlify replaces or merges
## same-named headers. Keep in sync with the /* CSP above (only `frame-ancestors *`
## differs). Widget pages are static calculators — no auth, no PII — so allowing
## any embedder is intentional.
/widgets/iframe/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self' https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://unpkg.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://tagmanager.google.com https://js.stripe.com https://*.supabase.co https://connect.facebook.net https://www.clarity.ms https://*.clarity.ms; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://unpkg.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com data:; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://www.google-analytics.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://lh3.googleusercontent.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://twemoji.maxcdn.com https://*.googleapis.com https://*.supabase.co https://www.facebook.com https://connect.facebook.net https://unpkg.com https://*.basemaps.cartocdn.com https://i.ytimg.com https://img.youtube.com https://yt3.ggpht.com https://*.ggpht.com https://static-cdn.jtvnw.net https://static-cdn.kick.com https://files.kick.com https://kick.com https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; connect-src 'self' https://*.netlify.app https://*.netlify.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://region1.google-analytics.com https://analytics.google.com https://www.google.com https://fonts.googleapis.com https://fonts.gstatic.com https://open.er-api.com https://api.frankfurter.app https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://api.coingecko.com https://api.coincap.io https://zpclagtgczsygrgztlts.supabase.co https://*.supabase.co wss://*.supabase.co https://api.anthropic.com https://*.googleapis.com https://www.facebook.com https://connect.facebook.net https://www.clarity.ms https://*.clarity.ms https://c.bing.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; frame-src https://js.stripe.com; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; frame-ancestors *; form-action 'self' https://formspree.io; upgrade-insecure-requests
