## Internal/source paths denied by redirects. These headers are defense in depth
## for accidental root-publish or stale deploy configuration.
/package.json
  Cache-Control: no-store
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, noarchive

/package-lock.json
  Cache-Control: no-store
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, noarchive

